Source: Nomenclature of NZ Fish
Author: SORENSON
Vol / Page: 32
Edition:
Quote: <i>KINGFISH, SILVER </i> (a) Scientific name: <i>Rexea solandri</i>. (b) Suggested commercial name[s]: Silver Kingfish; Silver King. (c) Other common names: Southen Kingfish. (d) Principal localities where taken: Cook Strait, Nelson, Lyttelton, Akaroa, Timaru.
